<section class="page-section">
  <h1>Buyer Onboarding Workflow</h1>

  <ol>
    <li><strong>Inquiry:</strong> Buyer contacts us with product, volume, location, and timeline.</li>
    <li><strong>KYC:</strong> Submission of LOI, corporate profile, incorporation documents, ID, and POF.</li>
    <li><strong>Product Confirmation:</strong> Agreement on product, volume, delivery method, and inspection.</li>
    <li><strong>Pricing:</strong> Official quotation issued with full breakdown.</li>
    <li><strong>Contracting:</strong> SPA drafted, reviewed, and signed.</li>
    <li><strong>Execution:</strong> Logistics, inspection, loading, and delivery.</li>
    <li><strong>Post‑Delivery:</strong> BOL, SGS report, certificate of origin, invoice.</li>
    <li><strong>Long‑Term Partnership:</strong> Priority processing and dedicated account management.</li>
  </ol>
</section>
